name: Luxurious log cabin
description: This luxurious log cabin was designed and built exclusively for couples. Whether you are a brand new couple or you've been together for 50 years, we'd love to have you spend time in our romantic cabin.

name: Old Hill Cider House
description: Welcome to Old Hill Cider House! Located just steps away from the first row of Summer Rambo Apple Trees at Showalter's Orchard. The thoughtful renovation was just completed in early July.

name: Beach hut
description: Of course, we do not expect you to spend all of your beach vacation indoors so we have provided beach cruisers, stand up paddleboards, body boards and an array of beach toys. While you are less than 50 yards from the beach, we also provide a wagon so you can pack your toys for an easy jaunt to one of the best beaches on could ever hope to enjoy.
